sequenceDiagram
    participant SCH as APScheduler 07:00
    participant ORCH as run_all_agents
    participant DES as Designer
    participant MKT as Marketer
    participant GEM as Gemini Nano Banana
    participant CLD as Cloudinary
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    SCH->>ORCH: scan owner
    ORCH->>DES: scan for each vacant unit
    DES->>GEM: design listing graphic
    GEM-->>DES: image bytes
    DES->>CLD: upload, get URL
    DES->>DB: cache unit.listing_graphic_url
    ORCH->>MKT: scan, reuse graphic
    MKT->>DB: insert telegram/ig/fb actions with image_url
    ORCH->>DB: plus Sales / Finance / Operations / HR actions
    Note over ORCH,DB: auto-safe actions execute, the rest await approval
